data.description: $10K SELLER CASH CONCESSION ON THIS 3/2 NAVIGABLE CANAL HOME OFF NORTH BANANA RIVER DRIVE ON MERRITT ISLAND!!! Open concept and beautifully remodeled in 2020 with new kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, appliances, bathroom vanities, AC, duct work, & hot water heater. The medium oak look luxury vinyl plank, white cabinetry and stainless appliances provide the perfect coastal palette with simple yet trendy pendants lights & fixtures, and the turquoise subway tile POPS! The home offers a generous 384 SF screened-in porch for added living space & the large backyard has plenty of room for a pool.  A circular driveway can accommodate multiple cars and a boat. Roof 2018. Excellent schools. NO HOA! Plus there is a 1-car garage. Cash Buyers can leverage with 3.375% assumable $194K Balance FHA.
